      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Anthropic Chat Model\n\nChat model powering the AI step (model: `claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929`). Swap providers here without rewiring.\n\nFeeds **Answer from Knowledge Base** as `languageModel`\n\n🔑 Anthropic API key",
